<subSubSection id="A7CC2DBDFFD0FFFBFF6BFC9BFBD9FB24" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="EF697E36FFD0FFFBFF6BFC9BFD5FFBE4" blockId="10.[151,1127,893,1268]" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD0FFFBFF6BFC9BFEBBFC24" bold="true" box="[151,261,893,916]" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFD0FFFBFEF5FC9BFE2AFC24" author="WEISE" box="[265,404,893,916]" firstAuthor="WEISE" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" pagination="1 - 205" refId="ref52379" refString="WEISE J. 1921: Wissenschaftliche Ergebnise der Swedischen Entomologischen Reisen des Herrn Dr. A. Roman in Amazonas und Bahia 1914 - 15 und 1923 - 24. 6. Chrysomelidae. Arkiv for Zoologi 14 (1): 1 - 205." type="journal article" year="1921">WEISE (1921)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD0FFFBFDFEFC9BFD64FC24" authorityName="Weise" authorityYear="1921" box="[514,730,893,916]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="obnubilata">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD0FFFBFDFEFC9BFD64FC24" box="[514,730,893,916]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">Metriona obnubilata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from a single specimen and compared it to 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD0FFFBFF39FC7BFD92FC04" authority="(Erichson, 1847)" baseAuthorityName="Erichson" baseAuthorityYear="1847" box="[197,556,925,948]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="glaucovittata">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD0FFFBFF39FC7BFECCFC04" box="[197,370,925,948]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">M. glaucovittata</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFD0FFFBFE83FC7BFD9DFC04" author="Erichson" box="[383,547,925,948]" firstAuthor="Erichson" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" pagination="67 - 185" refId="ref49195" refString="ERICHSON G. F. 1847: Conspectus insectorum coleopterorum, quae in republica Peruana observata sunt. Archiv fur Naturgeschichte 30: 67 - 185." type="journal article" year="1847">Erichson, 1847</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFD0FFFBFDC8FC7BFD57FC04" author="BOROWIEC" box="[564,745,925,948]" firstAuthor="BOROWIEC" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" pagination="203 - 222" refId="ref48049" refString="BOROWIEC L. 1989: Three new species of Charidotella Weise (Coleoptera, Chrysomelidae, Cassidinae), with checklist of the genus. Polskie Pismo Entomologiczne 59: 203 - 222." type="journal article" year="1989">BOROWIEC (1989)</bibRefCitation>
transferred it to 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD0FFFBFC6FFC7BFF72FC64" authority="Weise, 1896" authorityName="Weise" authorityYear="1896" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Charidotella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD0FFFBFC6FFC7BFBA5FC04" box="[915,1051,925,948]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">Charidotella</emphasis>
Weise, 1896
</taxonomicName>
and the taxon was listed only in catalogues (see 
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFD0FFFBFD1FFC5BFC27FC64" author="BOROWIEC" box="[739,921,957,980]" firstAuthor="BOROWIEC" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" refId="ref48283" refString="BOROWIEC L. 1999 a: A world catalogue of the Cassidinae (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae). Biologica Silesiae, Wroclaw, 476 pp." type="book" year="1999" yearSuffix="a">BOROWIEC 1999a</bibRefCitation>
). The 
<typeStatus id="306DC094FFD0FFFBFC21FC5BFB84FC64" box="[989,1082,957,980]" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">holotype</typeStatus>
has a pattern on the underside of elytra forming lateral stripe on each elytron and a band across elytra in their basal third. It also has subangulate humeral angles, a diffuse brownish pattern on pronotal disc and the specimen is conspecific with the 
<typeStatus id="306DC094FFD0FFFBFCFAFBFBFCDDFB84" box="[774,867,1053,1076]" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD0FFFBFC74FBFBFC4BFB84" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[904,1013,1053,1076]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Coptocycla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fumosa">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD0FFFBFC74FBFBFC4BFB84" box="[904,1013,1053,1076]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">C. fumosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD0FFFBFBFFFBFBFEB5FBE4" authorityName="Weise" authorityYear="1921" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="obnubilata">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD0FFFBFBFFFBFBFEB5FBE4" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">Metriona obnubilata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is thus synonymized with the latter species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EF697E36FFD0FFFBFF49FBBBFBD9FB24" blockId="10.[151,1127,893,1268]" pageId="10" pageNumber="285">
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFD0FFFBFF49FBBBFEDDFBC4" author="BOHEMAN" box="[181,355,1117,1140]" firstAuthor="BOHEMAN" pageId="10" pageNumber="285" refId="ref47955" refString="BOHEMAN C. H. 1855: Monographia Cassididarum. Tomus Tertius. Officina Norstedtiana, Holmiae, 543 pp. + 1 pl." type="book" year="1855">BOHEMAN (1855)</bibRefCitation>
did not state exactly how many specimens he had at his disposal. However, based on the original description and the single length measurement, I assume he had only one.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
